  <h1
    class="text-center text-lg bg-blue-200 border-b-2 border-black font-bold w-full"
  >CHAT IN REAL TIME
    <span
      class="animate-ping absolute mt-2 ml-1 h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-sky-400 opacity-75"
    ></span>
    <span
      class="relative inline-flex rounded-full ml-1 h-3 w-3 bg-sky-500"
